','Il Giardino Cinese è considerato uno dei giardini di più alto rango al di fuori della Cina.','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zurich_natur_und_sport_parks_gaerten_chinagarten_02.jpg','2019-04-04 17:52:31 +0200',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'CH','Zürich',8008 ,'Bellerivestrasse 138','www.stadt-zuerich.ch/chinagarten',47.354982608537,8.552089288886,'POINT (47.354982608537 8.552089288886)',8,'+41 44 380 31 51','<p>19. März bis Ende Oktober 2016<br>Täglich 11.00 &ndash; 19.00 Uhr</p>','<p>March 19 to end of October, 2016<br>Daily 11.00am &ndash; 7.00pm</p>','<p>Du 19 mars à fin octobre 2016<br>Tous les jours 11h &ndash; 19h</p>','<p>Dal 19 marzo a fine ottobre 2016<br>Tutti i giorni 11.00 &ndash; 19.00</p><p>&nbsp;</p>','Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday,Sunday','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zurich_natur_und_sport_parks_gaerten_chinagarten_02.jpg','Outdoors','Chinagarten - Der Tempelgarten am See
